Business Central allows managing up to 7 levels of hierarchy. Below is an example.

<img width="" src="https://docs.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000593-0/img4.png"><br>

The customer hierarchy type field (Enum) can be extended to allow other types of hierarchy (custom). Multi-hierarchies can thus be defined within the same item.

